        "observed_type": "image_caption",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "兔爷（泥塑） 现代 北京",
        "bbox": [
          0.03935026309768932,
          0.3873697916666667,
          0.2571493937314116,
          0.40234375
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991_0",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "兔爷是北京中秋节民 俗的标志之一，是一种人身兔 的泥玩具。这种别具匠的 造型，表现出北京的浪漫心 性和乐观幽默的性格。",
        "bbox": [
          0.036604895904827274,
          0.4036458333333333,
          0.2809425760695493,
          0.4765625
        ],
        "order": 6
